# Frontend environment variables
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# VITE_API_URL has been intentionally removed.
# In production Express serves the frontend from the same origin — all API
# calls use relative paths (e.g. /api/auth/login) and no absolute URL is
# needed.
# In development the Vite proxy in vite.config.js forwards /api and /auth
# to http://localhost:3000, so again no absolute URL is needed here.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------